headline: How Recent Developments Are Shaping the Nasdaq Investment Story
summary: Nasdaq's fair value estimate has experienced a minor decrease, falling from $102.67 to $102.35 as analysts digest recent developments and revise their outlooks. The modest shift reflects both the optimism generated by strong results in certain business areas as well as ongoing caution about uneven performance across key segments. headline: How Nasdaq's (NDAQ) Private Markets Data Partnership With LSEG Is Reshaping Its Investment Story
summary: On November 6, 2025, LSEG announced a partnership with Nasdaq to distribute institutional-grade private markets intelligence through LSEG's Workspace and Datafeeds, licensing Nasdaq eVestment™ datasets and integrating private market benchmarks into LSEG's ecosystem. This collaboration builds on LSEG's September 2025 launch of the UK's first Private Securities Market, highlighting growing industry focus on enhancing transparency and data coverage in private markets.
